Episodes.Actors: Gordon Ramsay, Jason Santos, Christina Wilson
Episodes.Plot: Disaster strikes when raw chicken and cold steak are served but one team reigns supreme and is rewarded with a swanky Hollywood rooftop pool party while the losing team picks up pieces of confetti one by one.

Episodes.Actors: Gordon Ramsay, Jason Santos, Christina Wilson
Episodes.Plot: The contestants must create elevated American comfort food dishes.

Episodes.Plot: Its time for Surf and Turf relay challenge where the chefs will taste and identify mystery proteins. The losers have to break down entire salmon for dinner service while the winners spend some quality time with Chef Ramsay.

Episodes.Title: All up in Your Grills
Episodes.Actors: Gordon Ramsay, Jason Santos, Christina Wilson
Episodes.Plot: Chefs tackle a high-stakes barbecue challenge with Aaron Franklin as the judge, then serve a star-studded dinner.

Episodes.Actors: Gordon Ramsay, Jason Santos, Christina Wilson
Episodes.Plot: Jordan Chiles challenges chefs to create balanced pasta dishes for Chef Evan Funke. Alix Klineman and Kel Mitchell guests and Some chefs excel as leaders with creative pasta, while others struggle and fall short.

Episodes.Actors: Gordon Ramsay, Jason Santos, Christina Wilson
Episodes.Plot: A new blind food taste test challenge arises. Scallop and soufflé problems at dinner service reveal winners and losers. Kitchen pressure mounts at the dinner service for The People Concern and Teen Cancer America.

Episodes.Plot: Ramsay gives black jackets to the aspiring chefs. They play craps to pick dishes for the initial challenge, the first of three that will determine who deserves to join the upper echelon.

Episodes.Actors: Gordon Ramsay, Jason Santos, Christina Wilson
Episodes.Plot: The chefs compete in a Hell's Kitchen Grand Prix challenge with a twist. At dinner service, Ramsay tests if they can run the kitchen with his tricks. Guests will see who takes the checkered flag and who falls flat.
